00:41:35,826 --> 00:41:38,871
I will not disappear over the horizon.

522
00:41:43,250 --> 00:41:44,418
No matter what.

523
00:41:54,345 --> 00:41:57,348
PATERNITY TEST
PROBABILITY OF PATERNITY: 99.999 %

524
00:41:57,932 --> 00:41:59,350
Well, of course.

525
00:42:01,060 --> 00:42:02,645
That's why she's so beautiful.

526
00:42:03,604 --> 00:42:04,438
Shit.

527
00:42:18,911 --> 00:42:20,371
HA YE-SOL

528
00:42:22,289 --> 00:42:24,542
Good afternoon, Hye-jeong.

529
00:42:24,625 --> 00:42:25,459
Hi.

530
00:42:25,543 --> 00:42:28,212
Someone from Information was here.

531
00:42:28,963 --> 00:42:31,799
- They found my cell phone?
- That's not why he came.

532
00:42:32,341 --> 00:42:34,718
It's thin. Urgent delivery for you.

533
00:42:34,802 --> 00:42:35,636
Urgent?

534
00:43:28,772 --> 00:43:30,024
Now you know.

535
00:43:31,191 --> 00:43:33,944
I dedicated my whole life to revenge.

536
00:43:45,456 --> 00:43:48,959
And you won't stop?

537
00:43:50,461 --> 00:43:53,297
You're better than them, Dong-eun.

538
00:43:55,841 --> 00:43:57,468
I don't intend to be better.

539
00:43:58,719 --> 00:44:00,095
I'm getting worse every day.

540
00:44:00,679 --> 00:44:02,348
When you're done with revenge,

541
00:44:03,557 --> 00:44:05,559
and your world will be destroyed.

542
00:44:24,662 --> 00:44:26,246
I envy you, Yeo-jeong.

543
00:44:26,914 --> 00:44:29,333
You must have had an idyllic childhood.

544
00:44:29,416 --> 00:44:31,710
You grew up and became good and happy.

545
00:44:32,544 --> 00:44:35,673
Sometimes you sound naive,
but you have no problems in life.

546
00:44:39,802 --> 00:44:41,011
You saw my scars.

547
00:44:48,686 --> 00:44:50,104
Can you remove them?

548
00:44:59,029 --> 00:45:00,531
How long has it been?

549
00:45:09,206 --> 00:45:11,041
You made such an expression

550
00:45:12,584 --> 00:45:13,919
after just one hand.

551
00:45:15,379 --> 00:45:16,213
And despite that

552
00:45:17,423 --> 00:45:18,674
do you want me to stop?

553
00:46:13,145 --> 00:46:14,521
The nights were white,

554
00:46:16,273 --> 00:46:19,359
and sometimes polar.

555
00:46:27,451 --> 00:46:28,786
They are guilty?

556
00:46:30,788 --> 00:46:31,789
That's what they did to you?

557
00:46:34,291 --> 00:46:35,709
Those bastards?

558
00:46:36,460 --> 00:46:40,380
I'm already devastated. I have no more dignity.

559
00:46:41,465 --> 00:46:42,966
Come back.

560
00:46:44,259 --> 00:46:47,513
I would like to remain faithful
to his anger and vice.

561
00:47:01,360 --> 00:47:02,528
I will do it.

562
00:47:05,072 --> 00:47:06,490
I will be your executioner.

563
00:47:10,744 --> 00:47:11,912
I will dance with a sword.

564
00:47:14,581 --> 00:47:15,707
Tell me.

565
00:47:16,792 --> 00:47:18,001
What's first?

566
00:47:19,086 --> 00:47:20,546
How do I do that?

567
00:47:23,507 --> 00:47:24,675
Who do you want...

568
00:47:27,511 --> 00:47:29,012
to kill first?

569
00:49:33,387 --> 00:49:38,392
Subtitle translation: Davor Fröbe


